homeDescribe:
L'Escale offers a place of rest, in a wooded setting, on the ULM aeronautical base of Gevigney.
Discover the calm of the Haute-Saone, in a newly renovated house offering all the amenities to preserve your privacy. 
Whether to walk or enjoy a bike, many places of walks will allow you to enjoy this corner of greenery, a perfect time to reconnect with nature!
Whether you are in ULM by car or by bike, we welcome you!
-
Alban and Patricia Causin
